  "text": "It is the contention of [CITATION_1] that Honesty/Humility be added as an independent factor to the Five Factor model as a measure of an individual's level of sincerity, fairness, greed avoidance and modesty, dimensions of personality that are not embedded in or measured by any other trait on the Five Factor model [CITATION_2] .",
